data.description: Welcome to this stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bath home nestled in the picturesque Rainbow Lake Estates. Situated on an expansive .66-acre lot, this residence offers a perfect balance of comfort and style just step inside to discover an inviting open floor plan that seamlessly connects the main living spaces providing comfort for entertaining or an intimate setting.  The home's split bedroom floor plan ensures privacy and tranquility for all. With an expansive Master bedroom with an on-suite bathroom and two additional bedrooms that will provide ample space for family members or guests, making this home ideal for accommodating loved ones. Outside, the enchanting beauty of Rainbow Lake Estates surrounds you, offering a serene and peaceful atmosphere. The .66-acre lot provides plenty of space for outdoor activities, BBQ's, gardening, or simply enjoying the natural surroundings. Whether you're hosting gatherings or seeking peaceful solitude, the outdoor space is a true benefit and rare find. Experience the perfect blend of comfort, style, and natural beauty this home has to offer. The Rainbow River gives you almost 6 miles of crystal blue waters allowing you ample opportunity for swimming, kayaking and canoeing or if you prefer just relax at one of the local waterfront restaurants.  The Rainbow Lake Estates has a community dock for fishing, a playground and pavilion specifically for the homeowners.  It is the perfect location for those commuting to Gainesville or Ocala allowing you to enjoy the quiet rural setting or a short drive to enjoy the World Equestrian Center and conveniently located to all the major medical facilities as well. Schedule your private showing today and make this wonderful property your new home.
